snippet.title: Whiskerwood - Announcement Trailer | Cats & Mice City-Builder Game
snippet.description:
In Whiskerwood, establish a home for your industrious mice in uncharted territory under the oppressive paw of their cat overlords in Whiskerwood - a city builder featuring complex simulations, supply chain management dealing with over 40 commodities, and the age-old rivalry between cat and mouse.

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2489330/Whiskerwood/
